"bb_ul\"><li> Choose from 6 routes based on the 6 seasons of India to make it to the final boss </li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A surprise ending can be achieved based on player's actions at the game's end </li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Many more options and ways to play depending on your preference and play style </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256860/extras/65b95ad91b1447d4ef4d0e37fd597dff.poster.avif?t=1770425681\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256860/extras/65b95ad91b1447d4ef4d0e37fd597dff.webm?t=1770425681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
